snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Over 3 Million Copies Sold!
snippet.description:
It started as one brave adventurer setting out to explore the Far, Far Range. Today, we’ve sold over 3 million copies of Slime Rancher. Thank you for sharing the story of Beatrix LeBeau with us 💖
